      <p begin="01:31.230" end="01:35.950" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="01:31.230" end="01:31.600">人</span><span begin="01:31.600" end="01:31.900">間</span><span begin="01:31.900" end="01:32.110">じゃ</span><span begin="01:32.110" end="01:32.310">な</span><span begin="01:32.310" end="01:32.440">い</span><span begin="01:32.440" end="01:32.630">っ</span><span begin="01:32.630" end="01:32.870">て</span><span begin="01:33.280" end="01:33.640">気</span><span begin="01:33.640" end="01:33.980">づ</span><span begin="01:33.980" end="01:34.340">い</span><span begin="01:34.340" end="01:34.660">て</span><span begin="01:34.660" end="01:35.010">い</span><span begin="01:35.010" end="01:35.240">た</span><span begin="01:35.240" end="01:35.530">ん</span><span begin="01:35.530" end="01:35.660">で</span><span begin="01:35.660" end="01:35.950">しょ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其实你已经察觉到我不是人类了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ningen janai tte kizuite itandesho</span></p>
      <p begin="01:36.360" end="01:38.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="01:36.360" end="01:36.550">い</span><span begin="01:36.550" end="01:36.730">が</span><span begin="01:36.730" end="01:36.870">み</span><span begin="01:36.870" end="01:37.000">合</span><span begin="01:37.000" end="01:37.240">う</span><span begin="01:37.240" end="01:37.410">の</span><span begin="01:37.410" end="01:37.540">が</span><span begin="01:37.540" end="01:37.910">正</span><span begin="01:37.910" end="01:38.270">解</span><span begin="01:38.270" end="01:38.430">な</span><span begin="01:38.430" end="01:38.660">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果互相敌视才是正确答案的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Igamiau no ga seikai nara</span></p>
