      <p begin="02:28.150" end="02:30.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="02:28.150" end="02:28.510">寂</span><span begin="02:28.510" end="02:28.690">し</span><span begin="02:28.690" end="02:28.890">く</span><span begin="02:28.890" end="02:29.020">な</span><span begin="02:29.020" end="02:29.190">い</span><span begin="02:29.190" end="02:29.340">よ</span><span begin="02:29.340" end="02:29.660">今</span><span begin="02:29.660" end="02:29.990">更</span><span begin="02:30.100" end="02:30.280">もう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经不寂寞了哦 事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sabishikunai yo imasara mou</span></p>
