      <p begin="02:33.140" end="02:38.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="02:33.140" end="02:33.310">だ</span><span begin="02:33.310" end="02:33.460">か</span><span begin="02:33.460" end="02:33.570">ら</span><span begin="02:33.690" end="02:33.840">も</span><span begin="02:33.840" end="02:33.990">う</span><span begin="02:35.860" end="02:36.040">テ</span><span begin="02:36.040" end="02:36.200">レ</span><span begin="02:36.200" end="02:36.370">パ</span><span begin="02:36.370" end="02:36.710">シー</span><span begin="02:36.710" end="02:36.860">に</span><span begin="02:36.860" end="02:37.030">気</span><span begin="02:37.030" end="02:37.180">づ</span><span begin="02:37.180" end="02:37.380">い</span><span begin="02:37.380" end="02:37.540">た</span><span begin="02:37.540" end="02:37.740">振</span><span begin="02:37.740" end="02:37.900">り</span><span begin="02:37.900" end="02:38.050">し</span><span begin="02:38.050" end="02:38.250">て</span><span begin="02:38.250" end="02:38.410">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以就装作已经察觉到了心灵感应吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara mou terepashii ni kizuita furi shite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:38.550" end="02:41.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="02:38.550" end="02:38.790">そ</span><span begin="02:38.790" end="02:38.940">の</span><span begin="02:38.940" end="02:39.100">目</span><span begin="02:39.100" end="02:39.270">か</span><span begin="02:39.270" end="02:39.430">っ</span><span begin="02:39.430" end="02:39.620">ぽ</span><span begin="02:39.620" end="02:39.790">じ</span><span begin="02:39.790" end="02:39.950">っ</span><span begin="02:39.950" end="02:40.110">て</span><span begin="02:40.110" end="02:40.270">気</span><span begin="02:40.270" end="02:40.620">づ</span><span begin="02:40.620" end="02:40.810">い</span><span begin="02:40.810" end="02:40.980">た</span><span begin="02:40.980" end="02:41.360">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你睁大眼睛察觉到了的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me kappojitte kizuitara</span></p>
      <p begin="02:41.650" end="02:44.860" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50"><span begin="02:41.650" end="02:42.180">心</span><span begin="02:42.180" end="02:42.300">の</span><span begin="02:42.300" end="02:42.620">内</span><span begin="02:42.620" end="02:42.790">を</span><span begin="02:42.790" end="02:43.120">荒</span><span begin="02:43.120" end="02:43.360">ん</span><span begin="02:43.360" end="02:43.470">で</span><span begin="02:43.700" end="02:44.020">送</span><span begin="02:44.020" end="02:44.220">っ</span><span begin="02:44.220" end="02:44.360">て</span><span begin="02:44.360" end="02:44.550">み</span><span begin="02:44.550" end="02:44.710">て</span><span begin="02:44.710" end="02:44.860">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就试着将这荒芜的内心发送过来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no uchi o susande okutte mite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:45.060" end="02:46.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L51"><span begin="02:45.060" end="02:45.230">飛</span><span begin="02:45.230" end="02:45.450">ば</span><span begin="02:45.450" end="02:45.580">し</span><span begin="02:45.580" end="02:45.740">て</span><span begin="02:45.740" end="02:45.910">み</span><span begin="02:45.910" end="02:46.070">て</span><span begin="02:46.070" end="02:46.230">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着让它飞翔吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tobashite mite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:46.390" end="02:48.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52"><span begin="02:46.390" end="02:46.600">そ</span><span begin="02:46.600" end="02:46.780">の</span><span begin="02:46.780" end="02:47.100">電</span><span begin="02:47.100" end="02:47.180">波</span><span begin="02:47.180" end="02:47.260">思</span><span begin="02:47.260" end="02:47.630">考</span><span begin="02:47.630" end="02:47.750">で</span><span begin="02:47.750" end="02:48.180">叫</span><span begin="02:48.180" end="02:48.310">ん</span><span begin="02:48.310" end="02:48.480">で</span><span begin="02:48.480" end="02:48.650">み</span><span begin="02:48.650" end="02:48.780">て</span><span begin="02:48.780" end="02:48.930">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着用那电波思考呼喊吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono denpa shikou de sakende mite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:49.170" end="02:51.550" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L53"><span begin="02:49.170" end="02:49.330">で</span><span begin="02:49.330" end="02:49.500">き</span><span begin="02:49.500" end="02:49.650">る</span><span begin="02:49.650" end="02:49.840">な</span><span begin="02:49.840" end="02:50.000">ら</span><span begin="02:50.000" end="02:50.360">今</span><span begin="02:50.360" end="02:50.500">も</span><span begin="02:50.500" end="02:50.850">笑</span><span begin="02:50.850" end="02:51.030">っ</span><span begin="02:51.030" end="02:51.370">て</span><span begin="02:51.370" end="02:51.550">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果可以的话现在也笑一笑吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dekiru nara ima mo waratte yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:51.870" end="02:54.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L54"><span begin="02:51.870" end="02:52.080">で</span><span begin="02:52.080" end="02:52.210">も</span><span begin="02:52.210" end="02:52.530">今</span><span begin="02:52.530" end="02:52.730">は</span><span begin="02:52.730" end="02:52.910">記</span><span begin="02:52.910" end="02:53.230">号</span><span begin="02:53.230" end="02:53.390">ば</span><span begin="02:53.390" end="02:53.570">か</span><span begin="02:53.570" end="02:53.760">り</span><span begin="02:53.760" end="02:54.080">で</span><span begin="02:54.080" end="02:54.400">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是即使现在全是符号</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Demo ima wa kigou bakari demo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:54.620" end="02:55.810" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L55"><span begin="02:54.620" end="02:54.970">愛</span><span begin="02:54.970" end="02:55.130">し</span><span begin="02:55.130" end="02:55.310">て</span><span begin="02:55.310" end="02:55.490">い</span><span begin="02:55.490" end="02:55.630">る</span><span begin="02:55.630" end="02:55.810">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也是爱着你的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aishiteiru no</span></p>
